      "review_summary": "Adds an `openclaw skills uninstall <slug>` command plus ClawHub lifecycle helpers to plan/remove workspace skill directories and `.clawhub/lock.json` entries, with dry-run, yes, json, global, and agent flags; the branch also currently adds `pr-body.md`.\n\nPR surface: Source +162, Tests +4, Docs +50. Total +216 across 4 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Source inspection of PR head shows the strict uninstall slug validation and missing uninstall assertions, while current main tests and helpers show owner-qualified and legacy tracked update behavior the new command should mirror.",
